OL,3,CMan charged over collapse of Ammanford
OL,4,Cschool stabbing trial
OL,6,FChristopher Elias, 45, from
OL,7,FWaunceirch, Neath Port Talbot, has
OL,8,Fbeen charged with the offence of
OL,9,Frefusing to answer a question relating
OL,10,Fto the qualification to serve on a
OL,11,Fjury.
OL,13,FHe appeared at Swansea Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt on 23 April, and will appear at
OL,15,Fthe court again on 14 May.
OL,17,FThe first trial involving the girl
OL,18,Fcollapsed in October 2024, because of
OL,19,Fwhat the judge described as a "great
OL,20,Firregularity in the jury".
